Usage:
    First, clone the repo on your home and cd in it:
        git clone https://github.com/Dan13615/dot-files ~/dotfiles/
        cd ~/dotfiles/

    To configure alacritty, run `stow alacritty`

    To configure bash, run `stow bash`

    To configure bumblebee-status, run `stow bumblebee-status`

    To configure fish, run `stow fish`

    To configure i3, run `stow i3`

    To configure i3status, run `stow i3status`

    To configure neofetch, run `stow neofetch`

    To configure remmina, run `stow remmina`

    To configure rofi, run `stow rofi`

    To configure scripts, run `stow scripts`

    To configure starship, run `stow starship`
